title: Bug 6322: All types dialog shows obfuscated classes
description: Bug 6322: All types dialog shows obfuscated classes. JDK 1.4 includes obfuscated classes like 'a', 'a1', 'b', 'c', 'd', etc.
OB: The All types dialog in the software is showing the obfuscated classes from JDK 1.4 more prominently.
EB: The obfuscated classes should be displayed with less prominence in the All types dialog.
SR: To reproduce the issue, open the All types dialog and observe the presence of obfuscated classes from JDK 1.4.
